import { Box, Button, Grid, TextField } from "@mui/material"; import React from "react"; import AddressCard from "../AdressCard/AddressCard"; import { Form, useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { useDispatch } from "react-redux"; import { createOrder } from "../../../state/order/Action"; const AddDeliveryAddressForm = () => { const dispatch = useDispatch(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const handleSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const data = new FormData(e.currentTarget) const address={ firstName:data.get("firstName"), lastName:data.get("lastName"), streetAddress:data.get("address"), city:data.get("city"), state:data.get("state"), zipCode:data.get("code"), phnNumber:data.get("phoneNumber") } const orderData = {address,navigate} dispatch(createOrder(orderData)) console.log("address", address); } return (
); }; export default AddDeliveryAddressForm;
